{
  "stem": "23506.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because see, I told you, he was a Bundist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at that time you have to go on Hashara.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, that you are prepared to this labor work, to work the-- the fields in the kibbutzim.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I said to my father, I am going to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father said, go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and then you will send me a certificate, and I will come.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, a lot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You-- a happy life, laughter, friendships, little love encounters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just little, you know, flirtations.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was-- it was lots of fun.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I had one boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I just didn't connect with him, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mentally.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was handsome looking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then something happened, I don't remember what.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My-- my husband, Mayer, was also a member in this Hashomer Hatzair club.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were the biggest enemies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I was-- he was a leading figure.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was leading among the girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we fought.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And soon fights changed into-- into love.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we both survived the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "From all the members in our group, which were 45, only 3 survived, or 4.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One girl went to Russia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Mayer went to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I went on Catholic papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I think one extra person came back from the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Everybody else was killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In my book, it is a combination, my father's influence, be gutsy, do, be risky.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he always told me how he-- he was-- he ran away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a deserter from the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and then the Hashomer Hatzair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- mt name of my book is,",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and my father said that the best way to survive is in the mouth of the wolf, which means under his nose, but watch not to be devoured.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
